{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22d5106ea3","title":"对召开军委扩大会议讨论军队缩编等问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d72de68e81","index":0,"year":1956,"month":11,"day":25,"articleId":"22d5106ea3"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"af03aeff8e","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长彭德怀1956年11月23日报告的批语。"},{"id":"970fcc1bfe","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。朱，指朱德。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"f8d011def6","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀呈送的中共中央军委《召开军委扩大会议的通知》说：决定于1957年1月初在北京召开军委扩大会议，讨论军队缩编问题和1957年的军队训练工作。随《通知》附送的《关于裁减军队数量加强质量的决定（草稿）》说：“军委决定：在裁减军队数量加强质量的原则下，把我军的现有的员额裁减三分之一，即从三百八十三万人中裁减一百三十万人左右，保持二百五十万人或者更少一些的常备军队。"}],"contents":[{"id":"83f4defc85","type":"title","text":"对召开军委扩大会议讨论军队缩编等问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3"},{"id":"af03aeff8e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、朱、陈、邓即阅。退彭照办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3"},{"id":"970fcc1bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3"},{"id":"f8d011def6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年十一月二十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3"}],"page":{"id":"87fa2ad7e8","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"22d5106ea3","start":153,"end":153}}}},"__N_SSG":true}